# Design System - Static Flow (Deep Focus)

## Color Palette

### Primary Colors (Use these exact hex values)
```dart
// lib/core/constants/app_constants.dart
class AppColors {
  // Backgrounds
  static const Color midnight = Color(0xFF1A1D26);  // Main background
  static const Color slate = Color(0xFF353B48);     // Card back, secondary surfaces
  
  // Brand Colors
  static const Color electric = Color(0xFF6C5CE7);  // Primary actions, buttons
  static const Color mint = Color(0xFF00CEC9);      // Accents, highlights, success
  
  // Text
  static const Color mica = Color(0xFFDFE6E9);      // Primary text
  static const Color textSecondary = Color(0xFF95A5A6); // Secondary text
  
  // Status Colors
  static const Color danger = Color(0xFFFF4757);    // Error, time warning
  static const Color success = Color(0xFF00CEC9);   // Same as mint
  
  // Opacity Variants (for overlays)
  static final Color overlay = midnight.withOpacity(0.95);
  static final Color cardOverlay = slate.withOpacity(0.3);
}
```

